Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:27.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Eu conheço a sua dor e solidão
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}Então, tudo que me completa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:36.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,580)\3c&H000000&}eu vou te dar isso agora
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:53.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Ah, por favor, me diga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:03:04.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}O vento agitou-se{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:11.46,OP,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Os dois se sobrepuseram{\i0}
